Decorative entities that hang on walls which come in 19 different variants.

Test structures that the player spawns inside upon loading a new world.
Removed after this version.
The player now has a hotbar and an inventory containing storage slots, armor slots and crafting slots, enabling players to carry more than one type of item at once.
You can now use items to craft new types of items.
You can now use a furnace to smelt items into new items.
There are now many different possible light levels, determined by time of day and proximity to light sources.
There is a now a sun and moon that cycle across the sky, and light levels change based on the time.
